            <h1>
              机械产品的信息化--面向机械装备的信息技术
            </h1>
            <h2>
              Informatization of Mechanical Product--Some Information Techniques for Mechanical Equipment
            </h2>
            <div id="ctl00_LeftContentPlaceHolder_periodical">
              <p id="fulltext" style="visibility:visible">
                <a href="/Service/File/view/机械产品的信息化--面向机械装备的信息技术.aspx?ID=Periodical_zggckx200411003" class="seeft">
                </a>
